亨利·罗林斯解释了为什么他再也不会创作音乐了https://www.nme.com/news/music/henry-rollins-explains-why-hell-never-make-music-again-3799584?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=henry-rollins-explains-why-hell-永远不再创作音乐Poppy BurtonFri, 04 Oct 2024 08:03:54 +0000 Music NewsNewsPunkhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3799584 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亨利·罗林斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不会安静地退出。我不会褪色。我只是在履行完所有义务后分手”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/henry-rollins-explains-why-hell-never-make-music-again-3799584">亨利·罗林斯 (Henry Rollins) 解释为何他再也不会创作音乐的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亨利·罗林斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/henry-rollins-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/henry-rollins">亨利·罗林斯</a>解释了为什么他再也不会创作音乐了，他说他“足够聪明，不会回来加演”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/backbeat-john-lennon-bisexuality-stuart-sutcliffe-3765319">30 岁的“Backbeat”：披头士第五乐队、约翰·列侬的双性恋和 Macca 的“嫉妒”</a><br /></b></li></ul><p>在短暂担任硬核乐队 State of Alert 的主唱后，罗林斯于 1981 年至 1986 年间继续担任加州硬核乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-flag">Black Flag</a>的主唱。乐队解散后，他成立了 2.13.61 唱片公司和出版公司，并组建了罗林斯乐队，并在各种乐队的带领下进行了巡演。 1987年的阵容。</p><p>这位朋克偶像涉足激进主义、广播主持、表演、演讲和口语领域，自从离开音乐界后，罗林斯的注意力仍然集中在写作上。周二（10月1日），他发布了他的<em>《Stay Fanatic!!!》</em>最新书！系列，<i>保持狂热！！！卷。 4 – 占有的教训和痴迷的忏悔</i>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-S0ItavdNE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.86